#we will use gmail credentials for sending the mail from server.


1.Install ssmtp & mailutils
2. Update /etc/ssmtp/ssmtp.conf
3. Allow less secure apps
4. https://www.google.com/accounts/DisplayUnlockCaptcha
5. ssmtp receiver@gmail.com < msg.txt OR mail -s 'subject' receiver@gmail.com <<< "Message"
